         <head>
            <ce:title id="tm005">Spatial patterns of seedlings dominated by proximity to deadwood and adult trees for <ce:italic>Pinus flexilis</ce:italic> and <ce:italic>Pinus longaeva</ce:italic>
            </ce:title>
